Chat 可以访问 Bing 搜索，因此可以比其构建的系统提供更多最新信息，从而可以访问自该模型发布以来发生的事件的信息。训练有素。除了第三方浏览器访问之外，最新版本的必应聊天还将提供多模式搜索，这意味着用户将能够上传照片并让人工智能回答有关其内容的特定问题，以及稍后的黑暗模式-小时人工智能查询。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-bing-chat-is-available-in-chrome-and-safari-mobile-191240880.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-bing-chat-is-available-in-chrome-and-safari-mobile-191240880.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c0fe43df-d32f-4688-b7d5-6a2adcf362df</guid><dc:creator>安德鲁·塔兰托拉</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 07 Aug 2023 19:20:40 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691434964</ingested><modified> 2023-08-07T19:02:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Andrew Tarantola]]></category><media:content height="4023" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/41fe98e0-2b26-11ee-b8ef-46c1f512fa8a" width="6319"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4023" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/41fe98e0-2b26-11ee-b8ef-46c1f512fa8a" width="6319"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Microsoft B